        <item>
            <title>Copilot 现可免费用 ChatGPT o1，一个设定加强提升解答精确度</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/03/microsoft-copilot-integrates-gpt-o1/ai/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=microsoft-copilot-integrates-gpt-o1</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/03/microsoft-copilot-integrates-gpt-o1/ai/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 06:35:43 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[AI]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[ChatGPT]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[GPT-o1]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[microsoft]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Microsoft Copilot]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[openai]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1289641</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Microsoft 日前宣布免费开放 OpenAI 的 GPT-o1 推理模型 「Think Deeper」 予所有 Copilot 用户。GPT-o1 模型可利用深层思考，透过逐步生成推理过程来提升答案精确度，减少错误与低品质内容。</p><p>GPT-o1 的「Think Deeper」功能让 Copilot 能处理更复杂的问题。用户只需点击 Copilot 内的「Think Deeper」按钮，AI 便会从多个角度审视问题，并提供更全面的回应。由于此功能涉及深入推理，处理时间较长，回应可能需时 30 秒以上。Microsoft AI 总裁 Mustafa Suleyman 在 LinkedIn 表示：「所有 Copilot 用户均可免费使用 OpenAI 的世界级 GPT-o1 推理模型。」，鼓励用户亲身体验其强大功能。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1289660 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025020315738-694x376.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="376" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025020315738-694x376.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025020315738.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1289643" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025020312833-357x580.jpg" alt="" width="357" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025020312833-357x580.jpg 357w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025020312833.jpg 555w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 357px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.linkedin.com/posts/mustafa-suleyman_today-weve-made-think-deeper-free-and-available-activity-7290487808706715648-Hj3S">Mustafa Suleyman@LinkedIn</a></p><p>然而 Microsoft 宣布免费提供 GPT-o1 之际，也引起部分用户关注。ElectroNet 英国总监 James Crouch 在贴文回应指，在得悉 Microsoft Copilot 免费提供 GPT-o1 后 24 小时内，便收到 Microsoft 365 家庭版，订阅价格上调 31% 的通知，质疑 Microsoft 是否透过调整价格来间接转嫁成本，以「一手加价、一手免费」的策略平衡开支。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1289645" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025020313432-694x229.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="229" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025020313432-694x229.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025020313432.jpg 1102w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.linkedin.com/posts/mustafa-suleyman_today-weve-made-think-deeper-free-and-available-activity-7290487808706715648-Hj3S">Mustafa Suleyman@LinkedIn</a></p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://www.theverge.com/news/603149/microsoft-openai-o1-model-copilot-think-deeper-free">The Verge</a>、<a href="https://www.theregister.com/2025/01/31/microsoft_open_ai_reasoning_copilot/">The Register</a></p><p>======</p><p>加入 <a href="https://www.threads.net/@unwirehk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">unwire thread</a> 倾倾科技背后黑暗事</p><p>========</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
